            ],
            "weighting": "<dd>40%</dd>",
            "due_date": "<dd><p> 23/09/2026 1:00 pm</p></dd>",
            "learning_objectives": "L01, L02, L04",
            "mode": "Written",
            "category": "Essay/ Critique",
            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>You are a consultant who has been hired to help an organisation with a challenge that they are facing. In this task, you will describe the context of the organisational challenge, diagnose what the issue is, and apply theories and concepts from the course to demonstrate your understanding of the issue. </p>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
            "submission_guidelines": "<p>Artificial Intelligence (AI) and Machine Translation (MT) are emerging tools that may support students in completing this assessment task. Students may appropriately use AI and/or MT in completing this assessment task. Students must clearly reference any use of AI or MT in each instance.</p>",
            "deferral_or_extension": "<p>You may be able to <a href=\"https://my.uq.edu.au/information-and-services/manage-my-program/exams-and-assessment/applying-assessment-extension\">apply for an extension</a>.</p>",
            "late_submission": "<p>A <a href=\"https://policies.uq.edu.au/document/view-current.php?id=184\">penalty</a> of 10% of the maximum possible mark will be deducted per 24 hours from time submission is due for up to 7 days. After 7 days, you will receive a mark of 0.</p>",
            "additional_info": "<p>You may be able to <a href=\"https://my.uq.edu.au/information-and-services/manage-my-program/exams-and-assessment/applying-assessment-extension\">apply for an extension</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
            "assessment_detail_section_id": "assessment-detail-1",
            "assessment_title": "Group pitch",
            "special_indicators": [
                {
                    "special_indicators_class": "icon--how-youll-learn--multiple-circle icon-text--small",
                    "special_indicator_text": "Team or group-based"
                },
                {
                    "special_indicators_class": "icon--engineering-and-computing--laptop icon-text--small",
                    "special_indicator_text": "Online"
                }
            ],
            "weighting": "<dd>40%</dd>",
            "due_date": "<dd><p> 12/10/2026 - 19/10/2026</p>\n<p>\n</p><p>Presentations will be during scheduled class times.</p></dd>",
            "learning_objectives": "L01, L02, L03, L04, L05",
            "mode": "Oral",
            "category": "Presentation",
            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>Your team has been hired to help an organisation with an issue they are facing. You will need to work together to diagnose the issue, design an intervention, and propose an evaluation of that intervention. Each team member will need to present part of the pitch during class time, and the team will need to submit slides in advance of the presentation.</p>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
            "submission_guidelines": "<p>Artificial Intelligence (AI) and Machine Translation (MT) are emerging tools that may support students in completing this assessment task. Students may appropriately use AI and/or MT in completing this assessment task. Students must clearly reference any use of AI or MT in each instance.</p>",
            "deferral_or_extension": "<p>You may be able to <a href=\"https://my.uq.edu.au/information-and-services/manage-my-program/exams-and-assessment/applying-assessment-extension\">apply for an extension</a>.</p>",
            "late_submission": "<p>You will receive a mark of 0 if this assessment is <a href=\"https://policies.uq.edu.au/document/view-current.php?id=184\">submitted late</a>.</p>",
            "additional_info": "<p>You may be able to <a href=\"https://my.uq.edu.au/information-and-services/manage-my-program/exams-and-assessment/applying-assessment-extension\">apply for an extension</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
            "assessment_detail_section_id": "assessment-detail-2",
            "assessment_title": "Interview",
            "special_indicators": [
                {
                    "special_indicators_class": "icon--engineering-and-computing--laptop icon-text--small",
                    "special_indicator_text": "Online"
                }
            ],
            "weighting": "<dd>20%</dd>",
            "due_date": "<dd><p> 26/10/2026 - 30/10/2026</p>\n<p>\n</p><p>We will schedule individual interviews at a suitable time during Week 13. </p></dd>",
            "learning_objectives": "L01, L04, L05",
            "mode": "Oral",
            "category": "Reflection",
            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>Following your group pitch, you will complete a short individual interview with the course coordinator. The interview is an opportunity for you to demonstrate your individual understanding of the work your group presented, reflect on your contribution to the group process, and show that you can think critically and independently about the theories, concepts, and decisions that underpinned your pitch.</p>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
            "submission_guidelines": "<p>This task has been designed to be challenging, authentic and complex. Whilst students may use AI and/or MT technologies, successful completion of assessment in this course will require students to critically engage in specific contexts and tasks for which artificial intelligence will provide only limited support and guidance.</p>",
            "deferral_or_extension": "<p>You cannot defer or apply for an extension for this assessment.</p>",
            "late_submission": "<p>A <a href=\"https://policies.uq.edu.au/document/view-current.php?id=184\">penalty</a> of 10% of the maximum possible mark will be deducted per 24 hours from time submission is due for up to 7 days. After 7 days, you will receive a mark of 0.</p>",
            "additional_info": "<p>You cannot defer or apply for an extension for this assessment.</p>"
        }
    ],
